name: z3-4.12.1
body:
4.12.1 release

## Changes:

* 3012293c35eadbfd73e5b94adbe50b0cc44ffb83 update release script
* fcc1bb5da88999ec2ecfb316bca54660b0f46d6d updated release notes
* 7368f9f7d3185198fd6b66db483f75f83ab697d4 increase build version, better propagation in euf-egraph, handle assumptions in sat.smt
* c8f197d0ca32f7dce935db0cca2fd80777b87ae9 specify macos-11 in nightly to force os11 build
* dde5218b293075a2267b09fe33722da18691c721 fix mbqi value caching issue raised by Clemens and Martin
* d5fde2e578f5600a5b4fc2c969c8931941580d40 #6538
* 4f7f4376b8e9ee12685968ba63f2cec5d19e8962 fix bug in new core not detecting conflict, fix #6525, add tactic doc

This list of changes was [auto generated](https://dev.azure.com/z3build/Z3Build/_build/results?buildId=4696&view=logs).
